Contact.js.keyStrokeInfo:
Contact Us

Leave us a message:

<form 
          onSubmit={e=>sendMessage(e)} 
          className="contact__form">
            <input 
              value={inputs.name} 
              onChange={e=>handleInputChange(e)} 
              type="text" name="name" 
              placeholder="name" 
              title="Your name" 
              maxLength="50" 
              required/>
            <input 
              value={inputs.email} 
              onChange={e=>handleInputChange(e)} 
              type="email" name="email" 
              placeholder="email" 
              title="Your email" 
              maxLength="50" 
              required/>
            <textarea 
              value={inputs.message} 
              onChange={e=>handleInputChange(e)} 
              type="text" name="message" 
              placeholder="message" 
              title="Your message" 
              maxLength="550" 
              required/>
            <input 
              type="submit" 
              value="send message"/>
        </form>
